{"TRASH":[{"def":"That which is worthless or useless; rubbish; refuse.","pos":""},{"def":"Especially, loppings and leaves of trees, bruised sugar cane, or the like.","pos":""}],"TRASHILY":[{"def":"In a trashy manner.","pos":""}],"TRASHINESS":[{"def":"The quality or state of being trashy.","pos":""}],"TRASHY":[{"def":"Like trash; containing much trash; waste; rejected; worthless; useless; as, a trashy novel.","pos":""}],"TRASS":[{"def":"A white to gray volcanic tufa, formed of decomposed trachytic cinders; -- sometimes used as a cement.","pos":""}]}